transcript.sentence: In a frame in the lower right hand corner of the screen, the song exploring my world by descent freak is being interpreted by amber galloway, guy a go of amber g productions.
Using American sign language, she interprets the meaning of the Lyrics as well as the rhythm and the feel of the music.
The rest of the screen displays videos of deaf, blind individuals in a variety of settings.
A young male retrieve z from a chickens roost in a walk. In chicken coop, he places the eggs into a large wire basket.
A female teacher and a female student sit across from each other in a classroom, communicating in sign language.

They are sitting next to a large board being used as a monthly anticipation calendar. It is divided into columns and rows of squares, and sum of the squares are marked off with a diagonal slash through them. Mounted on each square is a piece of paper with pictures, braille and writing on it.
A close up of a female adult working with a male student is shown. They are sitting in front of an easel with a stack of white paper on it.
The teacher has used a black marker to draw an index finger, indicating up on the Top sheet of paper.

She uses her right hand and her index finger to point up toward the ceiling. The student places his hand under the same paper, where it is traced with the black marker and imitates the teachers gesture.
A male teacher and a male student sit side by side in the backseat of a van. They communicate using tactile sign language.
A female student explores a raised bed garden.
Using hand over hand guidance and adult female. And a young female student explored the belly of a horse.
An adult female greets a young male student. She is kneeling in front of him, and he is in a motorized wheelchair.
They shake their heads at each other and make funny faces.
A young toddler sits in her father's lap. She begins to clap, and using his hands in front of her, he starts doing a swirling motion that she begins to imitate. The child begins to laugh.
A male students. It's reading about mountains on a computer monitor.
A young boy plays on the floor with a train set. He connects individual tracks to Complete an oval shaped train track.
A male student plays a guitar. He sits across from an adult who is helping him hold the guitar.
A female student paints as an adult. Female supports the activity from behind.
A male student stands facing the ocean with his family at the railing of a fairy. The wind is blowing through their hair and they are smiling.
A young man is seen at work in a grocery store, collecting and replacing handheld shopping baskets.
A male adults, it's across from a female adult.
They are using tactile sign language to communicate with his hand over her hand. She makes the sign for lion.
Using his other hand, he repeats the sign and then asks her for clarification.
In response, she fingers spells l I o n and with a surprise look on his face, he finger spells it back to her.
A young boy sits at a dining room table with a plate in front of him.
His mother stands next to the table, holding a picture text communication book. He points to the symbol for the food he requests.
A boy and a harness climbs a rock wall.
A young girl explores a wind CHiME that is being held by an adult.
A teenage girl walks down her school's hallway. There are many students lining the walls on either side of her.
An adult female stands behind her, supporting her at the elbow as the student reaches out and high fives those around her.
A female intervenor and a student sit knee to knee during a tooth brushing routine.
A teenage female student wearing finger less gloves sits at a desk working at a large black matt.
The matt has several small pieces of paper containing braille letters of the alphabet on it. She moves the letters from one place to another.
A young boy uses his hands to explore a wall. As an adult female observes. As the boy moves along the wall, the adult moves obstacles out of the way.
A young man swims in a pool.
Exploring my world fades out and new instrumental rock music fades in.
The shot begins by showing a music mixing board and pans up to show two women reviewing the levels on a digital equaliser displayed on a computer monitor in front of them.
Above them, text appears reading, written and performed by crystal and daniel morales of the scent freak.
